title: Husam was just looking for publicity, says PAS veep
text:
More 
Parti Amanah Negara leader Husam Musa turned up at a PAS event earlier this week just to seek publicity for himself, a PAS leader says. 
PAS vice-president Mohd Amar Nik Abdullah said the incident should not have occurred as Husam was given time to explain the matter that was raised beforehand.
